y  after mities annual general meeting   jennifer is nonexecutive director at gmg plc the body which governs strategy and commercial operations of the guardian media group  she is also a member of council of the royal college of art and chair of its remuneration committee   until march  jennifer was executive vice president people for arm holdings plc the ftse global technology business and was an executive committee member with responsibility for people and internal communications activity  from august  to august  she was group people and culture director at ubm plc and was group hr director at emap plc from october  to august    jennifer has an msc hons from the university of oxford in english and french   it is confirmed that there are no further details to be disclosed pursuant to lr  r  to  and that jennifer does not currently hold any shares in the company    ends   for further information contact phil bentley chief executive mitie group plc t                     m                    e philbentleymitiecom   anna chen investor relations manager mitie group plc t                     m                    e annachenmitiecom   notes for editors     about mitie group mitie is a ftse  business providing facilities management real estate consultancy project management and a range of specialist services that connect people with innovation and technology in the workspace environment helping our clients create better places to work and saving them money we work in partnership with organisations to deliver longterm value offering a wide range of services  from real estate and energy consultancy compliance risk assessment and security systems to cleaning catering and environmental services we manage and maintain some of the nations most recognised landmarks for a range of bluechip public and private sector customers   find out more at wwwmitiecom this information is provided by rnsthe company news service from the london stock exchange  end  boasfffiafwseew quick links equ